0x561C060B.name: EXECUTE_COMMAND
0x561C060B.description: Depending on your use case you may need to use `add_acl resource.<your_resource_name> command.<command_name> allow` to use this native in your resource.

examples.code:
Citizen.CreateThread(function()
  -- stop the server after 1 minute
  Citizen.Wait(60000)
  ExecuteCommand("quit Shortlived")
end)
